<div class="hero-unit">
  <h1>T Accounts <small>Learning accounting, one T Account at a time</small></h1>

  <p>
    I'm currently studying to become an Accounting Technician and I'm having
    to learn a bunch of accounting concepts. I quite like to learn by coding:
    if I understand enough of a concept to write code that implements it, I
    probably know enough to pass the exam, too.
  </p>

  <p>
    This application implements worksheets full of T Accounts. You create a
    bunch of accounts, then you create a set of transactions going between
    those accounts. This allows you to model particular financial transactions
    and see the double entry bookkeeping effect.
  </p>

  <p>
    Plus, the combination of:
  </p>

