    <li><%= link_to 'Ruby on Rails', 'http://www.rubyonrails.org' %>;</li>
    <li>Twitter's <%= link_to 'Bootstrap CSS', 'http://twitter.github.com/bootstrap' %>; and</li>
    <li><%= link_to 'Heroku','http://heroku.com' %></li>
  </ul>
  
  <p>
    makes it ridiculously easy to build and share wee apps like this that even
    look pretty out the box.
  </p>

  <p>
    If all this sounds a little interesting, feel free to sign up. It's free
    and I promise I won't steal your data.
  </p>

